20 pages, 1 figure, 2 tables. This is a preliminary version;
  comments, criticisms and suggestions are welcome. arXiv admin note: text
  overlap with arXiv:math/0210143 by other authors

38 pages, to appear in Annual Review of Nuclear and Particle Science;
